      "updated": 1772154028652,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "recalculateProfile(items) -> ProfileUpdate\n\nOutputs: comprehensionCeiling, productionCeiling,\n  readingLevel, writingLevel (0-1 floats),\n  currentStreak, longestStreak\n\nR = (1 + elapsed / (9 * stability))^-1  (FSRS curve)\nTriggered: every 10th review + after conversation end",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "recalculateProfile(items) -> ProfileUpdate\n\nOutputs: comprehensionCeiling, productionCeiling,\n  readingLevel, writingLevel (0-1 floats),\n  currentStreak, longestStreak\n\nR = (1 + elapsed / (9 * stability))^-1  (FSRS curve)\nTriggered: every 10th review + after conversation end",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
