    {
      "id": "elem_225_f29515ad",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 752,
      "y": 2943,
      "width": 490.55999999999995,
      "height": 495.40000000000003,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "elem_221_bece2906"
      ],
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772154028652,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "ONLY package importable from ALL layers\nTypes and enums ONLY — no logic\n\nState Machine:\n  MasteryState, ReviewGrade, ReviewModality\n  ItemType (lexical|grammar|collocation|chunk|pragmatic_formula)\n  LearningModality, ContextType\n\nFSRS:\n  FsrsState { due, stability, difficulty, ... }\n\nCurriculum Spine:\n  SpineUnit, SpineItemRef, ChunkTrigger\n  UnitProgress, ChunkTriggerResult\n  CurriculumPlan, CurriculumRecommendation\n  KnowledgeBubble, LevelBreakdown\n\nIPC (desktop):\n  IPC_CHANNELS (50+ method constants)\n  IpcChannel (union type)\n\nAuth & Onboarding:\n  AuthUser, SelfReportedLevel, OnboardingResult\n\nPayloads:\n  ReviewSubmission, ReviewQueueItem\n  ConversationMessage, SessionPlan\n  PostSessionAnalysis, ExpandedTomBrief",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "ONLY package importable from ALL layers\nTypes and enums ONLY — no logic\n\nState Machine:\n  MasteryState, ReviewGrade, ReviewModality\n  ItemType (lexical|grammar|collocation|chunk|pragmatic_formula)\n  LearningModality, ContextType\n\nFSRS:\n  FsrsState { due, stability, difficulty, ... }\n\nCurriculum Spine:\n  SpineUnit, SpineItemRef, ChunkTrigger\n  UnitProgress, ChunkTriggerResult\n  CurriculumPlan, CurriculumRecommendation\n  KnowledgeBubble, LevelBreakdown\n\nIPC (desktop):\n  IPC_CHANNELS (50+ method constants)\n  IpcChannel (union type)\n\nAuth & Onboarding:\n  AuthUser, SelfReportedLevel, OnboardingResult\n\nPayloads:\n  ReviewSubmission, ReviewQueueItem\n  ConversationMessage, SessionPlan\n  PostSessionAnalysis, ExpandedTomBrief",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
